CSS is a styling language that specifies how the browser should render HTML content. Notion uses stylesheets for dependency components (e.g. code highlight) and uses inline styles generated by React to style their own UI.css: /* stylesheet */
tag {
  property: value;
}
 html: <!-- inline styles -->
<tag style="property: value;"></tag>

